Install git if it hasn't been installed previously:

	sudo apt-get install git


Download this package in the home directory:

	git clone https://github.com/AfonsoBernardino/i2c-system.git


Them execute make in the package root:

	make


After this the following binaries can be found in i2c-system/bin directory:

tool, hv, prec


Execute each one of them with the option -h to get help and usage instructions.
